---
<div class="hero pb-16 pt-16 grid gap-4 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="images basis-full sm:basis-1/2">
        <Image src={tylerPodcast} class="tyler-pod rounded-sm" alt="Tyler in front of microphone for podcast" />
    </div>

    <div class="images basis-full sm:basis-1/2">
        <h1 class="pb-4 antialiased">I help men <br /><b>develop the tools</b> to maneuver through lifeâ€™s bullshit.</h1>
